  "title": "refactor(configure): migrate to TypeScript",
  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis refactors `connectConfigure` and `configure` to TypeScript.\r\n\r\nThe changes are mainly type definitions which are as long as the source so Git thinks they're whole new files.\r\n\r\nI added some basic tests for the `configure` widget.\r\n\r\n## Result\r\n\r\n- I removed the widget scope pollution by moving `this._refine` to a variable.\r\n- The connector/widget are now typed",
